## Plugins

Only listing the ones with key mappings I use often

##### Telescope

:Telescope help_tags
<leader>fh          find help
<leader>fk          find keymaps
<leader>ff          find files
<leader>fs          find select telescope
<leader>fw          find current word
<leader>fg          find by grep
<leader>fd          find diagnostics
<leader>fr          find resume (last find)
<leader>f/          find current buffer
<leader><leader>    find existing buffers

##### LSP

grr                 goto references
grd                 goto definition
grt                 goto type definition
gO                  open document symbols (variables, functions, types, etc)
gW                  open workspace symbols
grn                 rename
gca                 goto code action (on errors, warnings, etc)
grD                 goto declaration

##### Autoformatting

<space>f            Autoformat

##### Autocompletion

<tab>               accept completion
<tab>/<s-tab>       move to right/left of your snippet expansion
<c-space>           Open menu or open docs if already open
<c-n>/<c-p>         Select next/previous item
<up>/<down>         Select next/previous item
<c-e>               Hide menu
<c-k>               Toggle signature help

